{"tid":1933104,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（推到UST南亞仔回應）點解有咁多人質疑你？","createTime":"2020-03-19T06:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T21:50:34.000Z","uid":216008,"like":52,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3efe0dabfe76d02f3268e911b192c342f55dcb4d","tid":1933104,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"你條仆街仔真係越睇越唔順眼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">（推到龍門冰室回應）點解有咁多人質疑你？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1932590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1932590</a></span><br />\n咁樣開個post以為你有啲咩獨家一手料啦<br />\n原來係自己睇完人地啲屌鳩龍既講法 就開個post叫龍門回應<br />\n仲要話<br />\n「好多曾經同龍門共事嘅人 甚至同行都屌佢 我想知發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且因為咁我仲冤柱咗幾個連登&amp;Facebook 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">乜事都唔知就叫人回應 你係on9定帶風向呀？？？？？</span><br />\n我真係好撚想問 其實你係邊撚個 可以咁撚大支野叫人回應？<br />\n成鳩日勿分化勿內鬥 我又想問點解今次唔係 龍門得罪ust南亞哥你啲咩呀？？？？<br />\n我開呢個post就擺撚到明針對你條仆街仔<br />\n因為你已經唔止第一次係咁 成鳩日陰啲陰啲屌鳩人港獨齋叫人撐真普選 你估真係無人會開post屌鳩你條陰濕閪？"},{"pid":"82ba663341bbdf30eb169b54062a73a8c0a75140","tid":1933104,"uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"「樓主可唔可以講下發生咩事？」<br />\n「好多曾經同南亞仔有來往嘅人都屌佢 我想知發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且因為咁我仲冤柱咗啲唔係五毛既會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"f5c74b77e2dcfb49be6d4219c0c0111d0e7eb4da","tid":1933104,"uid":142854,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply